a ss:Type="String">This text 'you' refers to a person that can either be male or female. If relevant for translation, please use the ‘localized string’ column for the male text and the ‘alternative localized string’ column for the female text.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ANIMAL_DISCIPLINE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Animal Discipline</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zdyscyplinowanie zwierzęcia</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7" ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ANIMAL_DISCIPLINE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UNIT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit is handled strictly, boosting its combat capabilities. Unit gains +{AnimalDisciplineHealth}[HP/] and {MoraleBonus}</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka jest trzymana krótko, co zwiększa jej zdolności bojowe. Jednostka zyskuje +{AnimalDisciplineHealth}[HP/] i {MoraleBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ANIMAL_DISCIPLINE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HERO_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Animals units in this hero's stack are more strictly handled and taken care of, giving Animal and Mounted units +{AnimalDisciplineHealth}[HP/] and {MoraleBonus}[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostki zwierząt w stosie bohaterki są traktowane surowiej, co daje zwierzętom i jeździe +{AnimalDisciplineHealth}[HP/] i {MoraleBonus}.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ta bohaterka jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
